WEBVTT

00:03.352 --> 00:05.386
What a wonderful day, thank you.

00:05.387 --> 00:06.820
Oh, we're glad
you had fun.

00:06.822 --> 00:09.322
Blue Icees and a trip
to The Container Store?

00:09.324 --> 00:11.958
It's like I died and went
to the post-mortem,

00:11.960 --> 00:16.363
neuron-induced hallucination
commonly mistaken as heaven.

00:16.364 --> 00:18.465
I still don't understand
why you bought that pill caddie.

00:18.467 --> 00:19.633
You're a young man.

00:19.635 --> 00:22.035
Age is a state of
mind, Leonard.

00:22.037 --> 00:24.104
In here I'm 90.

00:26.575 --> 00:29.509
Why are you taking
your bins over there?

00:29.511 --> 00:31.011
That's just where
I need them.

00:31.013 --> 00:33.013
You know, she doesn't have
a lot of closet space.

00:33.015 --> 00:35.048
What's wrong with your closet?

00:35.050 --> 00:36.583
Uh...

00:36.585 --> 00:38.318
Well, honey, you know,

00:38.320 --> 00:39.886
now that Leonard and I
are married,

00:39.888 --> 00:42.823
it kind of makes sense
that we actually live together.

00:42.825 --> 00:44.591
So that's all this day was?

00:44.593 --> 00:47.427
A plan to butter me up
before delivering bad news?

00:47.429 --> 00:49.429
Come on, buddy.
No, I thought we were friends.

00:49.431 --> 00:51.698
You asked for a sip of my Icee.

00:51.700 --> 00:54.768
If you had your own straw,
I might've said yes.

00:54.770 --> 00:58.338
Sheldon, please, we already
feel bad about this.

00:58.340 --> 01:00.307
You know what they don't sell
at The Container Store?

01:00.309 --> 01:02.909
Something large enough
to contain my disappointment.

01:04.813 --> 01:06.012
Although,

01:06.014 --> 01:08.982
if anyone did, it would be them.

01:08.984 --> 01:12.619
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

01:12.621 --> 01:15.956
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

01:15.958 --> 01:17.591
♪ The Earth began to cool ♪

01:17.593 --> 01:20.127
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

01:20.129 --> 01:22.796
♪ We built the Wall ♪
♪<i> We built the pyramids</i> ♪

01:22.798 --> 01:25.465
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

01:25.467 --> 01:27.367
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

01:27.369 --> 01:29.305
♪<i> Bang!</i> ♪

01:29.306 --> 01:33.306
<font color=#00FF00>♪ The Big Bang Theory 9x04 ♪</font>
